data.description: WALK IN WITH INSTANT EQUITY AND EXPERIENCE THE EPITOME OF RIVERSIDE LIVING IN A PEACEFUL SOUGHT OUT NEIGHBORHOOD, THAT OFFERS THE RARE COMBINATION OF SERENITY AND ACCESSIBILITY! PREPARE TO BE WOWED AS YOU STEP INSIDE THIS UPDATED 5-BEDROOM, 3-BATHROOM HAVEN ENCOMPASSING 3,123 SQUARE FEET OF LIVING SPACE. THE HOME'S CLEVER DESIGN MAXIMIZES THE USE OF OPEN LAYOUT ENSURING AMPLE ROOM FOR FAMILY AND GUEST TO GATHER AND ENTERTAIN. THE ALLURE CONTINUES OUTSIDE, WHERE A GENEROUSLY SIZED BACKYARD AWAITS YOUR ENJOYMENT. IMAGINE LAZY AFTERNOONS BASKING IN THE SUN OR ENTERTAINING UNDER THE STARS.LOCATION IS NEAR THE BANKS OF SCENIC JAMES RIVER, HUNTINGTON BEACH AND PARK, AND MARINERS' MUSEUM, THIS PROPERTY OFFERS A UNIQUE AND SERENE LIVING EXPERIENCE. DON'T MISS THE CHANCE TO MAKE 81 RIVERMONT DR. YOUR FOREVER HOME, WHERE LIFESTYLE, COMFORT, AND CONVENIENCE SEAMLESSLY COME TOGETHER. SCHEDULE A VIEWING TODAY! THIS LISTING PARAGRAPH HAS BEEN MODIFIED BY ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE.
